 The idakula Family Multi-instrumentalist and singer-songwriter Bez Idakula and wife Tito are celebrating their 7th year wedding anniversary today. The inspirational couple have been married for 7 years, and they have three kids together. He shared a sweet message on Instagram with cute photo of them from their wedding saying “Officially 7 years with @titoidakula today! Whoa!! This is to us and many more years to come in uncommon love, bliss, peace and many crazy exploits! Love you babe!” She also posted a photo of the family and wrote; “THIS NUMBER SEVEN! Wow!!! Excited for the future, grateful for the past. We are doing this marriage thing well @bezidakula. I am so proud of us! God remains our leader and may we continue to follow in obedience! Love you babe!!”